							<a href="http://candy.about.com/od/caramelrecipes/r/Double-Chocolate-Caramels.htm" data-component="expertLandingPageRecentArticles" data-source="ArticleSite_Latest" data-type="article.blurb" data-ordinal="12" class="article-blurb">If a little bit of chocolate is good ,then a lot of chocolate is better! Double Chocolate Caramels have a soft and chewy texture, and a great chocolate flavor.</a>
